{"tid":502169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子舉牌抗議廣場舞 勢要「用文明對抗不文明」","createTime":"2017-12-17T15:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T14:00:47.000Z","uid":732,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1742096b38dd8d326eeb7c594559e7087807e13e","tid":502169,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"「廣場舞」被西方媒體喻為中國大媽創造的三大世界發明之一，規模愈來愈大，廣場舞早已跳出廣場，音樂從早到晚都不停歇。<br />\n<br />\n大叔、大媽們跳得開心，但附近的民居就苦不堪言。在河南，有市民對舞者跳上行人道、自行車道看不過眼，決定要用文明的方式，感化這些不文明的人。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，河南鄭州人民公園的不雅尬舞又似乎死灰復燃，有人就索性拿著把關刀，稱要守護屬於群眾的健身場地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1584152418395905/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1584152418395905%2F&d=pPvdEGKV10J3HFLQn5UWZuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=5ba90ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1584152418395905/</a>"},{"pid":"4ae5b2b53552f00697da365e68b2b9ede7713da5","tid":502169,"uid":164163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"仲用關刀 攞泥頭車剷埋佢哋去一邊啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}